{{Lunisolar March}} '''March 14''' is the 14th day of the month {{ill|March (Lunisolar)|ja|3月 (旧暦)|lt=March|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 3rd month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Butsumetsu|ja|仏滅|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Enryaku|ja|延暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 19th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[800]] {{ill|April 11|ja|4月11日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Fuji-san|ja|富士山|12=draft|12=draft}} erupted (the Enryaku eruption). * [[Shōka]] 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1257]] {{ill|March 31|ja|3月31日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – The era name was changed from {{ill|Kōgen|ja|康元|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} to [[Shōka]]. * {{ill|Genroku|ja|元禄|12=draft|12=draft}} 14th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1701]] {{ill|April 21|ja|4月21日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – At the Matsunorō corridor of Edo Castle, the lord of the Akō Domain, {{ill|Asano Nagamasa|ja|浅野長矩|12=draft|12=draft}}, was fatally injured by high-Ranking retainers of {{ill|Yoshira Yoshinaga|ja|吉良義央|12=draft|12=draft}}; Nagamasa committed seppuku on the same day (the incident known as the Akō Incident). * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1868]] {{ill|April 6|ja|4月6日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – The 【Goka Jō no Oneshimon】 (Five Articles of the Imperial Oath) were promulgated, and discussions regarding the surrender of Edo ensued between {{ill|Katsu Kaishū|ja|勝海舟|12=draft|12=draft}} and {{ill|Saigō Takamori|ja|西郷隆盛|12=draft|12=draft}}.
== Births == * {{ill|Meio|ja|明応|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 6th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1497]] {{ill|April 16|ja|4月16日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Mōri Motonari|ja|毛利元就|12=draft|12=draft}}, a military commander (died [[1571]]). * [[Bunka]] 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1809]] {{ill|April 28|ja|4月28日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Shimazu Nariakira|ja|島津斉彬|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 11th lord of the Satsuma Domain (died [[1858]]).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Genroku|ja|元禄|12=draft|12=draft}} 14th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1701]] {{ill|April 21|ja|4月21日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Asano Nagamasa|ja|浅野長矩|12=draft|12=draft}}, lord of the Akō Domain (born [[1667]]). * {{ill|Kansei|ja|寛政|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1789]] {{ill|April 9|ja|4月9日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Miura Baien|ja|三浦梅園|12=draft|12=draft}}, a thinker (born [[1723]]).
