== Births == * {{ill|Meio|ja|明応|qq=}} 6th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} [[1497]] {{ill|April 16|ja|4月16日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Mōri Motonari|ja|毛利元就|qq=}}, a military commander (died [[1571]]). * [[Bunka]] 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1809]] {{ill|April 28|ja|4月28日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Shimazu Nariakira|ja|島津斉彬|qq=}}, the 11th lord of the Satsuma Domain (died [[1858]]).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Genroku|ja|元禄|qq=}} 14th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1701]] {{ill|April 21|ja|4月21日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Asano Nagamasa|ja|浅野長矩|qq=}}, lord of the Akō Domain (born [[1667]]). * {{ill|Kansei|ja|寛政|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1789]] {{ill|April 9|ja|4月9日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Miura Baien|ja|三浦梅園|qq=}}, a thinker (born [[1723]]).
