{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=三月十四|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 3월 14일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar March|qq=}} '''March 14''' is the 14th day of the month {{ill|March (Lunisolar)|ja|3月 (旧暦)|lt=March (Yayoi)|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, the 3rd month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} day is {{ill|Butsumetsu|ja|仏滅|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Enryaku|ja|延暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 19th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[800]] {{ill|April 11|ja|4月11日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Fuji-san|ja|富士山|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} erupted (the Enryaku eruption). * [[Shōka]] 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1257]] {{ill|March 31|ja|3月31日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – The era name was changed from {{ill|Kōgen|ja|康元|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} to [[Shōka]]. * {{ill|Genroku|ja|元禄|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 14th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1701]] {{ill|April 21|ja|4月21日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – At the Matsunorō corridor of Edo Castle, the lord of the Akō Domain, {{ill|Asano Nagamasa|ja|浅野長矩|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, was fatally injured by high-Ranking retainers of {{ill|Yoshira Yoshinaga|ja|吉良義央|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}; Nagamasa committed seppuku on the same day (the incident known as the Akō Incident). * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1868]] {{ill|April 6|ja|4月6日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – The 【Goka Jō no Oneshimon】 (Five Articles of the Imperial Oath) were promulgated, and discussions regarding the surrender of Edo ensued between {{ill|Katsu Kaishū|ja|勝海舟|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} and {{ill|Saigō Takamori|ja|西郷隆盛|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}.
== Births == * {{ill|Meio|ja|明応|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 6th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1497]] {{ill|April 16|ja|4月16日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Mōri Motonari|ja|毛利元就|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, a military commander (died [[1571]]). * [[Bunka]] 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1809]] {{ill|April 28|ja|4月28日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Shimazu Nariakira|ja|島津斉彬|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, the 11th lord of the Satsuma Domain (died [[1858]]).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Genroku|ja|元禄|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 14th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1701]] {{ill|April 21|ja|4月21日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Asano Nagamasa|ja|浅野長矩|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, lord of the Akō Domain (born [[1667]]). * {{ill|Kansei|ja|寛政|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1789]] {{ill|April 9|ja|4月9日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Miura Baien|ja|三浦梅園|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, a thinker (born [[1723]]).
