'''March 14''' is the 14th day of the month {{ill|March (Lunisolar)|ja|3月 (旧暦)|lt=March (Yayoi)|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/March (Lunisolar)|qq=}}, the 3rd month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} day is {{ill|Butsumetsu|ja|仏滅|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Butsumetsu|1=Butsumetsu|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q10886789}}.

== Events ==
* {{ill|Enryaku|en|Enryaku|qid=Q1373176|lt=Enryaku|1=Enryaku}} 19th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|800|en|800|qid=Q23677|lt=800|1=800}} {{ill|April 11|en|April 11|qid=Q2501|lt=April 11|1=April 11}}) – {{ill|Mount Fuji|en|Mount Fuji|qid=Q39231|lt=Fuji-san|1=Mount Fuji}} erupted (the Enryaku eruption).
* [[:en:Shōka|Shōka]] 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|1257|en|1257|qid=Q5504|lt=1257|1=1257}} {{ill|March 31|en|March 31|qid=Q2461|lt=March 31|1=March 31}}) – The era name was changed from {{ill|Kōgen|en|Kōgen|qid=Q1194242|lt=Kōgen|1=Kōgen}} to [[:en:Shōka|Shōka]].
* {{ill|Genroku|en|Genroku|qid=Q1325001|lt=Genroku|1=Genroku}} 14th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1701|en|1701|qid=Q6814|lt=1701|1=1701}} {{ill|April 21|en|April 21|qid=Q2525|lt=April 21|1=April 21}}) – At the Matsunorō corridor of Edo Castle, the lord of the Akō Domain, {{ill|Asano Naganori|en|Asano Naganori|qid=Q2866316|lt=Asano Nagamasa|1=Asano Naganori}}, was fatally injured by high-Ranking retainers of {{ill|Kira Yoshinaka|en|Kira Yoshinaka|qid=Q3132109|lt=Yoshira Yoshinaga|1=Kira Yoshinaka}}; Nagamasa committed seppuku on the same day (the incident known as the Akō Incident).
* {{ill|Meiji era|en|Meiji era|qid=Q3125096|lt=Meiji era|1=Meiji era}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1868|en|1868|qid=Q7717|lt=1868|1=1868}} {{ill|April 6|en|April 6|qid=Q2506|lt=April 6|1=April 6}}) – The 【Goka Jō no Oneshimon】 (Five Articles of the Imperial Oath) were promulgated, and discussions regarding the surrender of Edo ensued between {{ill|Katsu Kaishū|en|Katsu Kaishū|qid=Q700470|lt=Katsu Kaishū|1=Katsu Kaishū}} and {{ill|Saigō Takamori|en|Saigō Takamori|qid=Q310462|lt=Saigō Takamori|1=Saigō Takamori}}.

== Births ==
* {{ill|Meiō|en|Meiō|qid=Q1193841|lt=Meio|1=Meiō}} 6th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|1497|en|1497|qid=Q6702|lt=1497|1=1497}} {{ill|April 16|en|April 16|qid=Q2519|lt=April 16|1=April 16}}) – {{ill|Mōri Motonari|en|Mōri Motonari|qid=Q1156545|lt=Mōri Motonari|1=Mōri Motonari}}, a military commander (died {{ill|1571|en|1571|qid=Q6666|lt=1571|1=1571}}).
* {{ill|Bunka|en|Bunka|qid=Q1373146|lt=Bunka|1=Bunka}} 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1809|en|1809|qid=Q6919|lt=1809|1=1809}} {{ill|April 28|en|April 28|qid=Q2534|lt=April 28|1=April 28}}) – {{ill|Shimazu Nariakira|en|Shimazu Nariakira|qid=Q1143856|lt=Shimazu Nariakira|1=Shimazu Nariakira}}, the 11th lord of the Satsuma Domain (died {{ill|1858|en|1858|qid=Q7684|lt=1858|1=1858}}).

== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Genroku|en|Genroku|qid=Q1325001|lt=Genroku|1=Genroku}} 14th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1701|en|1701|qid=Q6814|lt=1701|1=1701}} {{ill|April 21|en|April 21|qid=Q2525|lt=April 21|1=April 21}}) – {{ill|Asano Naganori|en|Asano Naganori|qid=Q2866316|lt=Asano Nagamasa|1=Asano Naganori}}, lord of the Akō Domain (born {{ill|1667|en|1667|qid=Q7588|lt=1667|1=1667}}).
* {{ill|Kansei|en|Kansei|qid=Q1195131|lt=Kansei|1=Kansei}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1789|en|1789|qid=Q7772|lt=1789|1=1789}} {{ill|April 9|en|April 9|qid=Q2504|lt=April 9|1=April 9}}) – {{ill|Miura Baien|en|Miura Baien|qid=Q8192957|lt=Miura Baien|1=Miura Baien}}, a thinker (born {{ill|1723|en|1723|qid=Q6921|lt=1723|1=1723}}).

